386
00:22:07,025 --> 00:22:08,540
What's his plan?

387
00:22:10,140 --> 00:22:12,900
He also asked me to pass some words.

388
00:22:13,650 --> 00:22:14,600
He said,

389
00:22:15,000 --> 00:22:17,175
you don't want to
take over North Liang

