00:25:29,550 --> 00:25:31,275
Here are all the clues

458
00:25:31,825 --> 00:25:33,500
I've found

459
00:25:34,125 --> 00:25:35,450
during the investigation.

460
00:25:43,220 --> 00:25:45,060
