504
00:28:38,800 --> 00:28:39,925
I owe her

505
00:28:40,300 --> 00:28:41,275
my life.

506
00:28:42,700 --> 00:28:44,450
It's just the layout of barracks.

507
00:28:44,700 --> 00:28:45,900
Nothing confidential.

508
00:28:45,900 --> 00:28:47,420
