601
00:34:16,380 --> 00:34:17,825
Not anymore.

602
00:34:18,300 --> 00:34:19,260
Li Chungang.

603
00:34:19,260 --> 00:34:20,180
Deng Tai'e.

604
00:34:20,180 --> 00:34:21,250
Jian Jiuhuang.

605
00:34:21,620 --> 00:34:24,000
Top masters of swordplay
emerge without end.

606
00:34:24,980 --> 00:34:26,525
The Wu Family

607
00:34:26,820 --> 00:34:28,500
