608
00:34:28,500 --> 00:34:29,975
But it still has foundation.

609
00:34:31,340 --> 00:34:32,325
Foundation

610
00:34:32,620 --> 00:34:33,725
and family rules.

611
00:34:34,980 --> 00:34:36,225
Back in the time,

612
00:34:36,340 --> 00:34:38,650
Her Grace wasn't allowed
to be with General.

