00:42:02,700 --> 00:42:04,250
the beast is cornered.

755
00:42:04,675 --> 00:42:05,725
It's strange.

756
00:42:06,200 --> 00:42:07,200
Which beast dares to

757
00:42:07,500 --> 00:42:09,375
