00:43:51,700 --> 00:43:54,500
♪Moved by the moment we met♪

769
00:43:56,500 --> 00:43:59,260
♪In spite of thunder and lightning♪

770
00:44:00,300 --> 00:44:04,220
♪In spite of my falling♪

771
00:44:04,700 --> 00:44:07,460
♪When we are apart♪

